data.description: Welcome to your new home! This single-family beauty sits on a newly fenced corner lot, offering privacy and space. Inside, you'll find a split bedroom floor plan, dining room that features vaulted ceilings adorned with charming wood beams, a custom-designed open kitchen, a spacious living room w/ a custom bar. The generously sized screened-in patio is the perfect place to unwind or entertain, overlooking the sparkling saltwater pool - a true oasis. The backyard is perfect for hosting BBQs and creating lasting memories. What sets this home apart is the BRAND-NEW ROOF and gutters, installed in March 2023, offering peace of mind for years to come. Remarkably low HOA fee of just $315 for the entire year! Don't miss out on making it your own! SELLER CREDIT of $10,000 if closed by Jan 31, 2024.
